But smart money sees the 
market completely differently. 

30
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:35,200
They see every swing as having three critical 
zones - premium, fair value, and discount. 

31
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:40,960
Retail traders buy when price looks 
strong. They sell when it looks weak. 

32
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:48,320
Banks do the exact opposite. They buy 
discount and sell premium. Every single time. 

33
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:54,400
This next technique is worth more than most 
trading courses. Here's how the pros map this  

34
00:02:54,400 --> 00:03:01,840
