on TradingView. Draw it from the swing low  

35
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:12,640
that started the breakout, to the swing high.
The quarters appear instantly. 25, 50 and 75%.  

36
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:16,560
These aren't random numbers.
These are the exact levels  

37
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:23,440
institutions use to define value.
This entire range becomes your universe. The  

38
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:33,200
