expensive. The bottom 25% is discount - everything  

39
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:41,280
here is cheap. And right in the middle at 50%, 
that's fair value. That's the battleground. 

40
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:47,040
But most traders can't see these 
zones. They're invisible. Until now. 

41
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:53,440
Watch this - this is where it gets crazy. 
Look at any chart with this filter. You'll  

42
00:03:53,440 --> 00:04:02,480
