levels over and over. It bounces at 25% discount.  

43
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:09,920
It reverses at 75% premium. 
It fights at 50% fair value. 

44
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:17,200
The reason this works is pure psychology. When 
price is in premium, sellers have the advantage.  

45
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:23,520
They're distributing at expensive prices.
When price is in discount, buyers have the  

46
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:30,480
