And this creates our entire trading edge.  

47
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:36,720
While retail buys premium thinking it's 
"strong," we're selling into their buying. 

48
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:42,640
While they panic-sell discount thinking 
it's "weak," we're buying their fear. 

49
